From 599f224eb3f211d66beb4e483a0dd32c5dac6636 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: RivonClaw Vendor Replay <vendor-replay@rivonclaw.invalid>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 07:23:04 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] vendor(openclaw): allow disabling startup recovery

Why:
- RivonClaw receives customer-service retries from backend/Airflow rather than relying on local gateway replay.
- OpenClaw startup delivery recovery and interrupted-session recovery can overwhelm the single desktop gateway process when many customer-service deliveries or aborted WeChat sessions are queued.

Removal:
- Drop when upstream OpenClaw exposes first-class config for startup recovery policies or makes startup recovery budgeted enough for RivonClaw customer-service workloads.

Tests:
- vendor/openclaw/src/gateway/server-runtime-services.test.ts
- vendor/openclaw/src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.test.ts
- apps/desktop/src/infra/proxy/proxy-manager.test.ts
---
 src/gateway/server-runtime-services.test.ts   | 27 ++++++++++++++
 src/gateway/server-runtime-services.ts        | 18 ++++++++-
 .../server-startup-post-attach.test.ts        |  9 +++++
 src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.ts     | 37 +++++++++++++------
 src/gateway/server.impl.ts                    |  1 +
 5 files changed, 80 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

